&lt;p&gt;Assessment for learning: 10 principles. Assessment Reform Group, 2002&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a style="line-height: 1.231;" href="http://www.aaia.org.uk/content/uploads/2010/06/Assessment-for-Learning-10-principles.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;http://www.aaia.org.uk/content/uploads/2010/06/Assessment-for-Learning-10-principles.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
